						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/how-a-19th-century-german-anthropologist-planted-the-roots-for-nazi-racial-theories/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">How a 19th-Century German Anthropologist Planted the Roots for Nazi Racial Theories</h7>
